9. INTERPRETATION AND CONSTRUCTION

9.1 Good Faith Interpretation
This License shall be interpreted and construed in good faith to advance its
stated purpose: enabling safe, accountable, and human-supervised AI agent systems
while preventing misuse that could harm individuals or society.

9.2 Ambiguity Resolution
In case of ambiguity regarding whether a particular use is permitted, the following
test shall apply: Does the use materially increase human agency, safety, transparency,
and democratic control over AI systems, or does it enable systems of surveillance,
control, manipulation, harm, or deception? Uses falling into the former category
are presumptively permitted; uses falling into the latter are presumptively prohibited.

